column5: So happy for you! Celebrate the good news and remember this feeling! Don’t think about tomorrow  or if this will change just live in the moment right now right here :)

Take a shower feel clean, put in some
Cologne or perfume :)
Sending lots of love and support your way. I always think that all my loved Onésimo have lost live inside me and help to protect me. They feel so close to me that way :)
